{"tid":1701112,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"山寨版 AirPods Pro 唔計差電盒成本 只係50元人民幣！ iOS 也被騙倒！","createTime":"2019-11-09T00:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T05:27:26.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4efe173d78c370d6cbaff89d5c8eef4c0e64d248","tid":1701112,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T00:46:03.000Z","msg":"AirPods Pro 才推出了不久，不過中國華强北的工程師已經成功「破解」製成山寨版，而售價僅需人民幣 260 元。中國影音網站拆解山寨版 AirPods Pro，外觀上跟 Apple 的 AirPods Pro 非常相似，充電盒子跟正牌只是分别在 Designed by Apple 那行字，即使機背的那個配對按鍵、Lightning 端口也跟正品相同。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/china-airpods-pro.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2Fchina-airpods-pro.jpg&h=300fb77c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n耳筒方面，外觀不仔細看的確跟 AirPods Pro 相似。當打開充電盒子將耳筒取出進行配對，iPhone 竟然將它辨識成 AirPods Pro。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/chinaairpods3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2Fchinaairpods3.jpg&h=a7d3905c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所有東西也看似十分「高仿」，然而當拆解這件裝置的內部結構，才可看到濃烈的山寨感，例如充電盒子的接合位置看似金屬，其實只是膠加上銀色噴漆。電池上橙色膠狀物是橡皮泥，電池使用橡皮泥固定及填充和配重。<br />\n<br />\n這耳筒的成本約人民幣 50 元，你可以想像質素會有多好。因此，千萬不要網上一些來歷不明的「網店」會有便宜貨！"},{"pid":"477832e5394034d48df8d074a6a4ae1995ff514a","tid":1701112,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T00:46:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/chinaairpodspro3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2Fchinaairpodspro3.jpg&h=ab5dd095&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2019/11/08/airpods-pro-china/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2019%2F11%2F08%2Fairpods-pro-china%2F&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOBTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=7443640c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2019/11/08/airpods-pro-china/</a>"},{"pid":"b85443d2a7619c1b2ab7487063fbdfa7f1ca7bc8","tid":1701112,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T00:47:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/chinaairpods5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2Fchinaairpods5.jpg&h=61bc99db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f1b62416c267ee1177dd08342714072efc820a3","tid":1701112,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T00:56:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F2.jpg&h=ecb87d84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F29.jpg&h=436883ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F25.jpg&h=14c796e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b56bba8d9058ed82b716a18226e9fa2a0c16454e","tid":1701112,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:28:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4585801f4ee33fe58674171cb21a0200341f1c4b","tid":1701112,"uid":8776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:52:31.000Z","msg":"其實點解會有airpod popup notification？"},{"pid":"2f6f33eb99cb5501d1a50732f25891e81c470fb2","tid":1701112,"uid":20890,"